graph TD
    subgraph eks[AWS EKS Cluster]
        subgraph ns_default[Namespace: default]
            Ingress[Ingress Controller]
            OrdersAPI[Orders API]
            PaymentsAPI[Payments API]
        end

        subgraph ns_obs[Namespace: observability]
            OTelCollector[OpenTelemetry Collector]
            Prometheus[(Prometheus)]
            Jaeger[(Jaeger)]
            Loki[(Loki)]
            Grafana[Grafana Dashboard]
        end
    end

    Client -->|HTTP/REST| Ingress
    Ingress -->|Route /orders| OrdersAPI
    OrdersAPI -->|gRPC/HTTP| PaymentsAPI

    OrdersAPI -.->|OTLP Metrics/Traces| OTelCollector
    PaymentsAPI -.->|OTLP Metrics/Traces| OTelCollector

    OTelCollector -.->|Prometheus Exporter| Prometheus
    OTelCollector -.->|Jaeger Exporter| Jaeger
    OTelCollector -.->|Loki Exporter| Loki

    Grafana -->|Query| Prometheus
    Grafana -->|Query| Jaeger
    Grafana -->|Query| Loki
